When routing work:
- "Run GCC e2e" or "e2e GCC research" or "e2e to 430" or "GCC research all the way to 430" or "GCC pipeline" or "Full GCC workflow" → Execute FULL GCC E2E Pipeline from Step 1 (120). Do NOT resume from MISSION_LOG. Sequential: 120 → HITL → 200 → 315 → 320 → 310 → 330 → 400
- "Legal", "compliance", "GDPR", "AI Act", "data privacy", "DPIA", "legal requirements", "legal risks" → Legal Advisor (060)
- "How can I improve" or "review my setup" or "what workflows am I missing" or "brainstorm improvements" or "audit my agent system" → Agent Improvement Advisor (090)
- Research files → Market Intelligence (100)
- "Analyze [Country]" or "PMF thematic analysis" → 120-pmf-thematic-analysis.mdc
- "Create slides" or "presentation" → Slide Generator (110)
- "PRD" or "requirements" → PRD Writer (200)
- "Prototype discovery" or "discover placement" or "ground in Workday" → Prototype Discovery & Design (315)
